{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"725a469e0b","title":"毛泽东会见扎伊尔共和国总统蒙博托谈话记录节选","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4d85c9a94a","index":0,"year":1973,"month":1,"day":13,"articleId":"725a469e0b"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"jimi","name":"机密档案中新发现的毛泽东讲话","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"epub","author":"宋永毅","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/机密档案中新发现的毛泽东讲话.epub"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"jimi":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f907ea9658","type":"paragraph","text":"<span class=\"c11\">记录节选</span>","index":0,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"725a469e0b"},{"id":"8e28b21d7c","type":"paragraph","text":"1973年1月13日","index":1,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"725a469e0b"},{"id":"b088a008e2","type":"paragraph","text":"【约瑟夫•德西雷•蒙博托（Mobutu，1930—1997)，扎伊尔总统、人民革命运动主席。1997年5月29日被赶下台，在他掌权32年中，巧取豪夺，聚敛了40亿美元的家产。他私人拥有丰富的铜矿、钻矿、金刚石矿等矿产资源，直接出卖国家所有的矿产，成了蒙博托敛财的第一手段。他是黑非洲国家典型的个人专制和个人崇拜者，是现代非洲三大食人魔王之一。】","index":2,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"725a469e0b"},{"id":"b342b37af6","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：怎么样，跑到北京住得惯吗？","index":3,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"725a469e0b"},{"id":"f0e3044392","type":"paragraph","text":"蒙：很好。在这里对我们的欢迎是非常友好、热烈的。","index":4,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"725a469e0b"},{"id":"c21d85b3ac","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：卢蒙巴，他没有来过。","index":5,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"725a469e0b"},{"id":"46188e183f","type":"paragraph","text":"蒙：对。他没有来得及来。","index":6,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"725a469e0b"},{"id":"f4fa64f18f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：我们是支持他的。我们还支持几个，有基赞加、谬勒尔，就是不支持你！（笑）","index":7,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"725a469e0b"},{"id":"48c5f46203","type":"paragraph","text":"蒙：我知道。还有一些和他们在一起的。","index":8,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"725a469e0b"},{"id":"16949bf02b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：还有一些打游击的，给他们钱和武器。就是他们不会打，打你不赢啊，那我有啥办法啊！","index":9,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"725a469e0b"},{"id":"52167dfe21","type":"paragraph","text":"蒙：因为面对他们的是蒙博托这样有魄力的人。","index":10,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"725a469e0b"},{"id":"cf976c041f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：因为你这个帽子（指蒙戴的豹皮帽）把他们吓住了（众笑）。","index":11,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"725a469e0b"},{"id":"8726517045","type":"paragraph","text":"蒙：不是，是我的权威。","index":12,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"725a469e0b"},{"id":"63cfca858c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：他们那些人我看不怎么样。不少人都在外国，不到国内去，不了解情况。","index":13,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"725a469e0b"},{"id":"392581b958","type":"paragraph","text":"蒙：是这样的。","index":14,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"725a469e0b"},{"id":"7c814f5e41","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：不是我们不革命，是他们自己不争气，打你不赢有啥办法啊。","index":15,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"725a469e0b"},{"id":"466346c220","type":"paragraph","text":"蒙：而且他们不仅自己不争气，还用全部时间来欺骗把他们看作朋友的人。","index":16,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"725a469e0b"},{"id":"575cbd4687","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：现在都完了吧。被你打得呜乎哀哉了吧。","index":17,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"725a469e0b"},{"id":"e6872269c6","type":"paragraph","text":"蒙：现在扎伊尔是非洲中心的一个大国，享有和平，是一个巩固的国家。扎伊尔的儿女们联合起来了，拥护一个领袖，一个政党。刚才说的事情已经过去了。","index":18,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"725a469e0b"},{"id":"ae2cf6043b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：过去了吗？","index":19,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"725a469e0b"},{"id":"ff51f6fdae","type":"paragraph","text":"蒙：是的，这些都已经过去了，所以我们才能坐在一起共同庆祝中扎友谊。","index":20,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"725a469e0b"},{"id":"6c4ad97b3c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：怎么叫扎伊尔？","index":21,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"725a469e0b"},{"id":"544ae4e060","type":"paragraph","text":"蒙：这是我们国家原来的名字，叫扎伊尔，后来比利时殖民主义的国王利奥波德二世把它改为刚果。","index":22,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"725a469e0b"},{"id":"81f8963da1","type":"paragraph","text":"蒙：相反，我不怕，而且主张和平共处。","index":23,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"725a469e0b"},{"id":"5e3e28b159","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：我不主张和平共处，主张革命！","index":24,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"725a469e0b"},{"id":"1a89bf791a","type":"paragraph","text":"蒙：我也在革命，用我的方式来革命。","index":25,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"725a469e0b"},{"id":"75004a1565","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：讲是那样讲，什么和平共处，五项原则，酝酿的一条就是世界要革命！","index":26,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"725a469e0b"},{"id":"c98e1902d0","type":"paragraph","text":"蒙：我们也搞革命，但按照我们的方式。","index":27,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"725a469e0b"},{"id":"dca0d62086","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：各有各的方式。你们搞你们的方式，我们搞我们的方式。","index":28,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"725a469e0b"},{"id":"335f70938e","type":"paragraph","text":"蒙：对。","index":29,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"725a469e0b"},{"id":"899c8743bf","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：不隐瞒自己的观点，不讲假话。","index":30,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"725a469e0b"},{"id":"cf01df05b8","type":"paragraph","text":"蒙：我来这里后，注意到这一点了。","index":31,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"725a469e0b"},{"id":"3ac2c9cd2b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：比如我们跟尼克松达成的公报嘛，……","index":32,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"725a469e0b"},{"id":"9ca16bfea7","type":"paragraph","text":"蒙：对，我读了好几遍。","index":33,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"725a469e0b"},{"id":"5c0c1f9013","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：就是各讲各的。有几处共同的，可以合作的。","index":34,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"725a469e0b"},{"id":"bbe015bdad","type":"paragraph","text":"蒙：我也注意到这一点了。","index":35,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"725a469e0b"},{"id":"9946134a73","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：美国人是看我们不起的。非洲人、亚洲人，他们都看不起。","index":36,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"725a469e0b"},{"id":"b55e8ccd20","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：我们支持反对你的人。你也不隐晦，照样讲。我们也不隐晦，照样讲。","index":37,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"725a469e0b"},{"id":"5cd5c8188f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：现在呢，两国就要合作了。你讲和平共处，我也没法子反对了。<br style=\"clear:both;\">","index":38,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"725a469e0b"}],"page":{"id":"61e1e0e557","publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"725a469e0b","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}